
1  

Keanyu Balaam ebe etoiokit EJAKAIT aisirereŋ Isirael, mam abu kolot, kwape sek, airiamun kaieudeta, konye kiteteo akekonyen amodiŋ. 
2  Kiteluo Balaam akekonyen, koany Isirael iboiete kwape ajaatar atekerinikec; kobunok ŋes emoyo loka EJAKAIT. 
3  

Kiner akewaraga ebe,

“Inera Balaam okoku loka Beor,

Inera da etuŋanan loetumudakitai akekonye.


4  

Inera loepupi akiro nuka Edeke,

Loeanyuni etapo loka Lokapedor kere,

Ibirun, kokwenyete akekonye, ebe.


5  Ejokuka ca ma iwemanakon, wu Yakob,

Iwemanakon lukalaunak, wu Isirael!


6  

Elalak bala aditono,

Kwape kamanan nuka ariri naka ecor,

Kwape iluan luera EJAKAIT,

Kwape iresia kariri naka akipi.


7  

Eleleete akip kamotike,

Ejaununos ikinyomoke toma akipi nuipu,

Eojaar ekekabaka adepar Agag,

Itopoloorio da akejakanut.


8  Kitolom ŋes Edeke koMisiri;

Ejaas kagogoŋ kwape naka ekosobwan:

Enyami atekerin nuka lukasurupoke,

Emunyumunyei akecekojo.

Icumi kes kimaliake.


9  

Abu kodipidipakin, koper bala eŋatuny,

Bala aŋatuny; iŋai itonyouni ŋes?

Isirereŋio yenikilipakini jo arereŋ,

Ilamakinio yenikilamakini jo.”


10  Kinep anyunyura naka Balak aluikin Balaam, kibapak akekanin: kolimok Balak Balaam atiar, “Abu kanyarau jo aikenokin lukasurupoka, ido koany, ilipak kes arereŋ cut irwan nu auni. 
11  Aso do, koker aiboisikon: enerunit aitopoloor jo koraun lokaibuses; konye koany, kitikok EJAKAIT jo adumun aibuses.” 
12  Kotema Balaam Balak atiar, “Mam eoŋ abu kalimok ikonikiyakia da luibu kijukak ebe, 
13  ‘Karaida kainaki Balak eketogo ileleba epuesa ka esabu, mam apedori adepar akirot naka EJAKAIT, aswam nuejok arai nueroko nuaomit eoŋ eloper; nupeinera EJAKAIT, ŋupeŋun eneri eoŋ da’? 
14  Koany, alosi kwana mama ejaas ituŋaka: bia, kalimok jo nuepote ituŋa ŋul aiswamakin ikonituŋa kapaarasia nukakonyen.” 
15  Kiner akewaraga ebe,

“Inera Balaam okoku loka Beor ebe,

Inera da etuŋanan loetumudakitai akekonye:


16  Inera loepupi akiro nuka Edeke,

Loejeni da aijen naka Loejai kuju kakuj; Loeanyuni etapo loka Lokapedor kere, Ibirun, kokwenyete akekonye, ebe:


17  

Etei ŋes, konye mere kwana:

Aseseni ŋes, konye mere kodie:

Elomuni aacerit kotoma Yakob,

Ikeuni ebela loka ajakanut koIsirael, Iposi agorieik nuka Moab apedor, Ebili da odwe kere luka eŋuŋet.


18  

Eraun Edom nake,

Ka Seir da eraun nake, luaraas lukasurupoke;

Kiswamai Isirael nukagogoŋ.


19  Kotoma Yakob ŋes elomunia ekayaiton,

Emudiari da luideuna kore.”


20  Kite Amalek, kiner akewaraga ebe,

“Kerai Amalek nasodit naka atekerin;

Konye esaŋeke lokakonyen emudiario.”


21  Kite da Ekenit, kiner akewaraga ebe,

“Erai aibois naiboionono ijo naegogoŋ,

Ecinakina akaikon atiiba.


22  Kwabo icweio Kain

Aitodol nakinataria Asur jo.”


23  Kiner akewaraga ebe,

“Wu okwe, iŋai ejari naiswamaa Edeke ŋun?


24  

Konye epote imeerin kariri naka Kitim,

Epote aitican Asur, ka aitican da Eber,

Ŋes da emudiario.”


25  Konyou Balaam, koloto koboŋo aiboisike: kolot Balak da.

